author: dlr
msg: * Makefile.in
(check-javahl): Gate ability to execute "check-javahl" on whether
the --with-junit flag was passed to configure.
The JAVAHL_TESTS_TARGET preprocessor will be set by configure when
it was passed the --with-junit flag.  The "javahl" target uses this
token to build or avoid building the JUnit test cases, without
which the "check-javahl" cannot be run.  Use JAVAHL_TESTS_TARGET to
make this determination when "check-javahl" is executed to provide
improved feedback to the user attempting execution.
